<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.19">
<l>muṟṟilun tūtaiyum muṉkaimmēl pūvaiyuñ</l>
<l>ciṟṟi liḻaittut tiritaru vōrkaḷai</l>
<l>paṟṟip paṟittukkoṇ ṭōṭum paramaṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>ṉeṟṟi yiruntavā kāṇīrē nēriḻai yīrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Fine-jewelled Ladies, see the quality of the forehead of him,</l>
<l>who is the Supreme Being, who, having grasped the women</l>
<l>who were playing, building sand houses with a small winnow and toy pot</l>
<l>with Myna birds on [their] forearms, runs off! Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
